		<ul role="list" class="clients">
			<li><a href="https://inkfish.co.za/" target="_blank">Inkfish digital marketing</a></li>
		</ul>
		<hr />
		<h2>Final Note</h2>
		<p>
			While much of my portfolio showcases websites built from mockups provided by talented designers, this experience
			has refined my greatest strength: acting as the vital bridge between creative vision and technical execution. I
			excel at collaborating with designers who are masters of their craft in tools like Figma or Photoshop but may lack
			confidence in the web environment.
		</p>
		<p>
			My role has consistently been to take those static designs and breathe life into them, ensuring the final product
			remains true to the original intent while functioning flawlessly across devices. I thrive in team settings where I
			can partner with designers to solve layout challenges, optimise performance, and ensure accessibility, effectively
			turning their high-fidelity concepts into robust, user-friendly realities.
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong>
				Based on all this I hope for the possibility of discussing how my skills can contribute to your upcoming
				projects. Thank you for your time and consideration.
			</strong>
		</p>
		<hr />
		<h2>Contact Info</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Email: <a href="mailto:stefan@vivtec.co.za">stefan@vivtec.co.za</a></li>
			<li>Phone: <a href="tel:+27614315742">061 431 5742</a></li>
			<li>CV: <a href="/docs/cv_stefan_le_roux.pdf" target="_blank">Download</a></li>
			<li><em>Recommendation letter: <a href="/docs/stefan-leroux_rec-letter.pdf" target="_blank">Download</a></em></li>
		</ul>
		<hr />
	</article>
</LayoutCanvas>

<style>
	.clients {
		border-left: solid 5px #fff;
		padding-inline-start: 1em;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: start;
		flex-flow: row wrap;
		gap: 1em;

		> a {
			display: inline-block;
		}
	}

	article {
		width: min(1000px, 100%);
		margin-inline: auto;
		padding-block: 2rem;
		padding-inline: 2rem;

		a {
			font-weight: bold;
			text-decoration: underline;
			color: #fff;

			&:hover {
				color: blanchedalmond;
			}
		}

		> *:not(:where(:last-child)) {
			margin-block-end: 1em;
		}

		> *:not(h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6):has(+ :is(h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, hr)) {
			margin-block-end: 2.75em;
		}

		:is(ul, ol):not([role="list"]) li:not(:last-child) {
			margin-block-end: 0.5em;
		}

		li:has(> :is(ol, ul)) :is(ol, ul) {
			margin-block-start: 0.5em;
		}

		:is(h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6) {
			text-transform: uppercase;
			line-height: 1.1;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: var(--fs-6);
		}
		h2 {
			font-size: var(--fs-5);
		}
		h3 {
			font-size: var(--fs-4);
		}
		h4 {
			font-size: var(--fs-3);
		}

		hr {
			border: unset;
			border-top: dotted 5px;
		}
	}

	header {
		position: relative;
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
		display: grid;
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 3rem;
		place-items: center;
		border-radius: 2em;
		isolation: isolate;
		overflow: clip;
		background: #fff;
		margin-block-end: 2.5em;

		&::before {
			content: "";
			position: absolute;
			inset: 0;
			scale: 2;
			background:
				linear-gradient(90deg, color-mix(in oklch, #aaa, transparent 80%)) 60% 60% / 200px 200px no-repeat,
				linear-gradient(90deg, color-mix(in oklch, #aaa, transparent 80%)) 70% 20% / 200px 200px no-repeat,
				linear-gradient(90deg, color-mix(in oklch, #aaa, transparent 80%)) 50% 45% / 200px 200px no-repeat,
				linear-gradient(90deg, color-mix(in oklch, #aaa, transparent 80%)) 60% 40% / 200px 200px no-repeat;
			z-index: -2;
			rotate: 45deg;
		}

		&::after {
			content: "";
			position: absolute;
			inset: 0;
			background: radial-gradient(#ffffff 25%, transparent 25%) center center / 30px 30px;
			z-index: -1;
			mask: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, black 10%, transparent 80%);
		}
	}
	#fox {
		inline-size: min(400px, 100%);

		svg {
			inline-size: 100%;
			filter: drop-shadow(20px -15px 5px #00000080);
		}
	}

	h1 {
		inline-size: 100%;
		padding-block: 0.25em;
		padding-inline: 0.25em;
		background: #93a885;
		text-align: center;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 2em;
		corner-shape: squircle;
	}

	hgroup {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1em;

		h2 {
			text-wrap: balance;
		}

		p {
			font-size: var(--fs-3);
		}
	}
</style>
